         <abstract>
            <p>A rational approximation to Weierstrass' $\mathscr{P}$-function in the equianharmonic case for unit period parallelogram is given. With a third-degree numerator polynomial and a fourth-degree denominator polynomial the maximal error for |z| &lt; 1/$\surd \bar{3}$ becomes $3 \cdot$ 10$^{-14}$. The approximation of $\mathscr{P}(z)$ is then used to calculate a rational approximation to $\mathscr{P}'(z)$ together with an error bound.</p>
          </abstract>
